Problem Occurred During Project 4
Problems Occurred During Project
 
 
1. Dataset contains 355,511 records and very few columns (only 7). Due to big dataset with very few columns it was very difficult to show big story and to analyze the different dimension in depth.

2. There was no unique identifier key to differentiate the records on the original data set. Therefore, Composite key was used to make unique identifier.

3. Some ports have been closed and some were started between the period of the data was recorded. Therefore, average calculation of some ports is less reliable.

What are the most common problems in project management ? watch
